import React from 'react';
import { View, Text,TouchableNativeFeedback } from 'react-native';
import { ListItem } from 'react-native-elements'



export default function Account() {
    return (
        <View style={{ display: "flex", flex: 1 ,marginVertical:10}}>
            <TouchableNativeFeedback onPress={()=>{}}>
            <ListItem bottomDivider >
              
                <ListItem.Content>
                    <ListItem.Title>Create an account</ListItem.Title>
                    <ListItem.Subtitle>Create your own acount to make appointment</ListItem.Subtitle>
                </ListItem.Content>
                
                <ListItem.Chevron />
               
            </ListItem>
            </TouchableNativeFeedback>
            <TouchableNativeFeedback onPress={()=>{}}>
            <ListItem bottomDivider >
                <ListItem.Content>
                    <ListItem.Title>Log in</ListItem.Title>
                    <ListItem.Subtitle>Log in to find your bookings</ListItem.Subtitle>
                </ListItem.Content>
                <ListItem.Chevron />
            </ListItem>
            </TouchableNativeFeedback>
            <Text style={{margin:20}}>Setting</Text>
            <TouchableNativeFeedback onPress={()=>{}}>
            <ListItem bottomDivider >
                <ListItem.Content>
                    <ListItem.Title>Setting 1</ListItem.Title>
                    <ListItem.Subtitle>what to set for your account</ListItem.Subtitle>
                </ListItem.Content>
                <ListItem.Chevron />
            </ListItem>
            </TouchableNativeFeedback>
            <TouchableNativeFeedback onPress={()=>{}}>
            <ListItem bottomDivider >
                <ListItem.Content>
                    <ListItem.Title>Setting 2</ListItem.Title>
                    <ListItem.Subtitle>what to set for your account else?</ListItem.Subtitle>
                </ListItem.Content>
                <ListItem.Chevron />
            </ListItem>
            </TouchableNativeFeedback>
            <Text style={{margin:20}}>Appointment history</Text>
            <TouchableNativeFeedback onPress={()=>{}}>
            <ListItem bottomDivider >
                <ListItem.Content>
                    <ListItem.Title>Check your appointment history</ListItem.Title>
                    <ListItem.Subtitle>Check what clinic did you booked with</ListItem.Subtitle>
                </ListItem.Content>
                <ListItem.Chevron />
            </ListItem>
            </TouchableNativeFeedback>
           
        </View>
    );
}
